5个月前自己换电池粘的胶松了，想重新粘一下，闲的没事想给因为装的k80电池导致的缝隙打点硅脂，刚拆开主板盖板，就明显感觉到摄像头那块（松动）然后摄像头就只有主摄能用了，长焦和广角都不识别，明明图2的三个排线都安上了，还是不行&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/HyperOS3?type=0&quot;&gt;#HyperOS3#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/312bcdfe1958a8fb35f4ddd31bada278.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/d9f8bcfc2008d8ecd8b3ab08d0f3c70f.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70758782</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70758782</guid><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 12:34:02 GMT</pubDate><author>OutMamba</author></item><item><title>酷友们，把这风扇改装成桌面制冷风扇有搞头吗[受虐滑稽] #共田F95D# #DIY#</title><description>&lt;p&gt;酷友们，把这风扇改装成桌面制冷风扇有搞头吗[受虐滑稽] &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E5%85%B1%E7%94%B0F95D?type=0&quot;&gt;#共田F95D#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/ff87c74820964422bc951d4f539ea9cc.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70756014</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70756014</guid><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 09:59:15 GMT</pubDate><author>IIIMissed_</author></item><item><title>【karen那个自走电脑怎么搞啊？怎么计划？】如题 #AI# #AI创造营# #DIY# 怎么先ai后这个，一般怎么慢慢合作的</title><description>&lt;p&gt;【karen那个自走电脑怎么搞啊？怎么计划？】如题 &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/AI?type=12&quot;&gt;#AI#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/AI%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E8%90%A5?type=12&quot;&gt;#AI创造营#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=12&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt; 怎么先ai后这个，一般怎么慢慢合作的&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70730109</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70730109</guid><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 01:57:05 GMT</pubDate><author>helloworld_kkk</author></item><item><title>第一次焊接，焊了个蓝牙音箱，我有点4了，焊的和鸟屎一样，[受虐滑稽]，最后失败了（插上电蓝牙模块不亮灯，直接用3.5㎜耳机线连接也没用，只会识别到耳机，不响...</title><description>&lt;p&gt;第一次焊接，焊了个蓝牙音箱，我有点4了，焊的和鸟屎一样，[受虐滑稽]，最后失败了（插上电蓝牙模块不亮灯，直接用3.5㎜耳机线连接也没用，只会识别到耳机，不响。开关竟然能控制我的电脑的拓展坞的开和关，我真没想到，废了废了），不知道哪个没焊好[喷血]，真吐血了，这么个小玩意耗了我一坤时，[汗]，累累累，&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/0f2eb64738f15885e9ab8342a783b927.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/11460187e2db90052181702d7cd1a4dc.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/0c4e0610a4b993950bb746612bd85f95.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/5b64e4bd2636928c3ae29d82a4192a9f.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70729020</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70729020</guid><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 00:30:37 GMT</pubDate><author>不里猫泰裤辣</author></item><item><title>#DIY# 第六款蓝牙音箱。</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;  第六款蓝牙音箱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/ee093c2315342c14edc83f25fceb04dc.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/32b213657fee66696c87e12b935282c6.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/d990369dba1ea4ccfc5b46ff988a7522.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/da92d537c832eb23e63fac3802ddd094.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/f156d7e3c1d709e3d26157efe487545e.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/0b56e815e6a1695000aaa954791731d5.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70724108</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70724108</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 13:46:23 GMT</pubDate><author>WANGMK</author></item><item><title>兄弟们，想买一个无头平板再配个屏幕，这个方案可行吗[呲牙] #DIY#</title><description>&lt;p&gt;兄弟们，想买一个无头平板再配个屏幕，这个方案可行吗[呲牙] &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/aa48116e8a39f0333af34fe6aae684ee.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/c0fbdc3f041a4434c6458114ef3dbc82.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70721330</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70721330</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 11:08:49 GMT</pubDate><author>二级厨师李二牛</author></item><item><title>DIY墨水屏手机壳，可永久显示不耗电，这次这个配色我是真喜欢呀#努比亚# #DIY# #墨水屏#</title><description>&lt;p&gt;DIY墨水屏手机壳，可永久显示不耗电，这次这个配色我是真喜欢呀&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E5%8A%AA%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A?type=0&quot;&gt;#努比亚#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/%E5%A2%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%8F?type=0&quot;&gt;#墨水屏#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/9ccd1aa4515921379480e8c3bd5bf875.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/3bfeea5d047a92d45d41c5ca5825e52e.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/b964213547faa21ec2b53c535d0029a1.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/df155292924516a849f19124b7187834.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70720830</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70720830</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 10:41:32 GMT</pubDate><author>赵不尤</author></item></channel></rss>